---
title: Sequence Diagram - Check-in Tamu
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor FD as Front Desk
    participant UI as Halaman /occupancy
    participant Act as Server Action checkIn
    participant DB as Supabase
    participant Notif as Toast Notification

    FD->>UI: Cari reservasi via booking_reference
    UI->>DB: SELECT * FROM reservations WHERE booking_reference = ?
    DB-->>UI: { reservation, guest, room }
    UI-->>FD: Tampilkan detail reservasi
    FD->>UI: Klik tombol "Check-in"
    UI->>Act: checkInReservation(reservationId)
    Act->>DB: UPDATE reservations SET status='checked-in', actual_check_in = NOW() WHERE id = ?
    DB-->>Act: ok
    Act->>DB: UPDATE rooms SET status='occupied' WHERE id = ?
    DB-->>Act: ok
    Act->>DB: INSERT INTO billing_items (reservation_id, room_id, amount, description='Room charge')
    DB-->>Act: ok
    Act-->>UI: { success: true }
    UI->>Notif: "Check-in berhasil"
    Notif-->>FD: Tampilkan notifikasi sukses
